This is my map called zm_concreteJungle. **THIS IS A BETA**
This map took me alot of time ^^. Put alot of detail into it.

File size: 1.9MB
Max Players: 64
Cubemaps: Yes
Vvis : Full
Vrad : Full
Type: ZombieMod
Detail : Moderate/extreme
FPS: 90
Author: sunshine



=== Background story. ===
 

Year, 2011.

Scientists have made a cure to AIDS, Cancer and other diseases.


Year, 2012

France, USA, GB, Italy, China and other world leading countries started vaccinating every inhabitant of they're country.


Year, 2015

Something was terribly wrong with the cure.
All vaccinated people are getting a desire for row meat, and blood.


Year, 2016.

All vaccinated individuals started to eat the unvacuolated people.


- - - - -
Name: Earl.
Age: 26.
Location of birth: Unknown.

That is you.
You were arrested by the police when zombies attacked the town.

Survive,
If you can.
